{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"metadata":{"title":"requestProgress","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)requestProgress","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/requestProgress":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress","title":"requestProgress","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackState/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate\/mlnofflinepackstateunknown","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"It is unknown whether the pack is inactive, active, or complete.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a region offline to a local database.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgre